languages.text: "Что ты несешь? Смеешь сравнивать свою жалкую душонку с моей, ксенос?! Зря, ох зря!" {n}В глазах Каллигоса непонимание и ярость. Похоже он сам еще не осознал свою истинную природу.{/n}

"What are you babbling about? You dare compare your pitiful soul to mine, xenos? Mistake, big mistake!" {n}You see confusion and fury in Calligos's eyes. It seems the Rogue Trader himself has yet to realise what he has become.{/n}

languages.text: “你在胡说些什么玩意儿呢，异形？你竟敢拿你可怜的灵魂和我相比！你错了，大错特错！”{n}你在卡里戈斯的眼中看到了困惑与愤怒。看来，眼前的行商浪人并没有意识到自己变成了什么样子。{/n}
languages.original_text: "What are you babbling about? You dare compare your pitiful soul to mine, xenos? Mistake, big mistake!" {n}You see confusion and fury in Calligos's eyes. It seems the Rogue Trader himself has yet to realise what he has become.{/n}

traits.locale_text: “你在说什么疯话，异形？你竟敢拿你可怜的灵魂和我相比！你错了，大错特错！”{n}在卡里戈斯的眼中，你看到了困惑与愤怒。看来，这个人还没有准备好认清自己的本性。{/n}
traits.speaker: Quetza-al_Winterscale

languages.text: « Qu'est-ce que vous racontez ? {mf|Un|Une} misérable xénos ose se comparer à moi ? C'est une erreur qui va vous coûter très cher ! » {n}La confusion et la fureur se lisent dans le regard de Calligos. Il semblerait que le libre-marchand n'ait pas encore pris conscience de ce qu'il est devenu.{/n}

languages.original_text: "What are you babbling about? You dare compare your pitiful soul to mine, xenos? Mistake, big mistake!" {n}You see confusion and fury in Calligos's eyes. It seems the Rogue Trader himself has yet to realise what he has become.{/n}
